<para>Worker function used for monitoring the FIFO position of the given device. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Actions depend on <computeroutput>mode</computeroutput>:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="_m_i_e_s___threaded_f_i_f_o_handling_8ipf_1ae93f07f22f4725c657d1b855465fddd9" kindref="member">TFH_RESTART_ACQ</ref>: Restart acquisition from the start</para>
