<para>Pushes the following entries into the thread queue:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>fifoPos: fifo position (relative to offset)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>startSequence: (yoking only) inform the main thread that ARDStartSequence() commmand should be called </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
